# IdentityDocumentProviderRegistrationStore.Status

**Enumeration**

Defines a status for the registration store.

## Declaration

```swift
enum Status
```

## Discussion

This value indicates whether the app is able to register documents with the system.

## Enumeration Cases

- **IdentityDocumentProviderRegistrationStore.Status.authorized**: The user has authorized the current app for document providing.
- **IdentityDocumentProviderRegistrationStore.Status.notAuthorized**: The user has not yet authorized the current app for document providing.
- **IdentityDocumentProviderRegistrationStore.Status.notDetermined**: The user has not made a choice in to the current app for document providing.
- **IdentityDocumentProviderRegistrationStore.Status.notSupported**: The current platform is not supported for document providing.

## Defining and getting the status of the mobile document

- **status**: The status of the registration store.

## Conforms To

- Copyable
- Equatable
- Hashable
- Sendable
- SendableMetatype
